{"tid":770307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國研究報告：常用美顏自拍app易患精神病","createTime":"2018-08-07T03:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T11:13:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32ef9fe066b016533ad7a68ad0c3f291ef3c3c86","tid":770307,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2130000/2131219/beauty_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2130000%2F2131219%2Fbeauty_1024.png&h=f0a54996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍照美顏App是不少女士必備的手機應用程式。英國《每日郵報》近日引述美國醫學院研究人員的文章，指頻繁使用拍照美顏App，有機會引發一種名為身體畸形恐懼症（Body dysmorphic disorder，BDD）的心理問題，是一種精神病。少女亦有機會因追求濾鏡中的自己而產生不斷整容的慾望。<br />\n<br />\n拍照美顏App並不罕見，年輕人常用的SnapChat及Instagram限時動態都有內置的自拍濾鏡，可讓瑕疵如雀斑、暗瘡消失得無影無蹤。波士頓大學醫學院（Boston Medical Center）研究人員近日於《美國醫學會雜誌・面部整形外科學卷》（ JAMA Facial Plastic Surgery）上發表文章，指以往只有名人或美容雜誌才會出現修圖，但隨着手機興起，Photoshop不再是演藝界人士的專利。<br />\n<br />\n該醫學院認為，拍照美顏App的普及，令美顏照全天候充斥社交媒體，恐會引發身體畸形恐懼症（Body dysmorphic disorder，BDD），影響年輕人的身心健康。<br />\n<br />\n身體畸形恐懼症與強迫症頗有關聯，患者會不斷追求外貌升級，亦會放大自己身上一個輕微的缺陷，主觀認為自己外表醜陋。他們或會因為此病而拒絕與其他人正常交往，亦會出現病態行為包括抓皮膚或不斷尋求整形等。《每日郵報》指，在美國，每50個人就有1個人受身體畸形恐懼症困擾。<br />\n<br />\n參與研究的Dr.Neelam Vashi，指出自拍文化及濾鏡（filters）、修圖app的流行，令不少年輕男女產生錯誤印象，容易對自己的面容感到不滿。她說，以往人們會要求整容後看來似某某明星，但近年開始，不少年輕男女會帶著使用美顏濾鏡後的相片，要求小修小補到跟相中人一模一樣，意味他們在真實生活中，亦希望看來似使用濾鏡後的模樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2131219/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A0%BB%E7%B9%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%A1%8F%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8Dapp%E3%80%80%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%93%E6%82%A3%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2131219%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E7%25B9%2581%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25A1%258F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%258B%258Dapp%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2582%25A3%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%2597%2585&d=HyTeR31y2n6e9uAjay0mD0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=fb87ce97\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2131219/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A0%BB%E7%B9%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%A1%8F%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8Dapp%E3%80%80%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%93%E6%82%A3%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85</a>"},{"pid":"e106bb62162418677eaa10f494bd48184e73e0ad","tid":770307,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:42:56.000Z","msg":"全篇主旨<br />\n豬西唔好扮上菜！"},{"pid":"e83b475be0b0d52e3f9534d3af630cd2b50ed96b","tid":770307,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"其實要食網上個kol, 總之自己要比人突出<br />\n已經係情緒病一種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5035da205bc1068401b256229d4f46888324c7bb","tid":770307,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd879ca83ef03a39dfb77e456f9ef6c79be80e3","tid":770307,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:55:11.000Z","msg":"好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e912cfd4de70f75427e470a345ff66d5f93c8d39","tid":770307,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾先鍾意"},{"pid":"9d05424c8dfce88da55c507b2e23a64ab683dd0b","tid":770307,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}